==============
3rd Party Code
==============

Some code distributed within testkraut was developed by 3rd parties, hence
you should adhere to the copyright and license terms of respective authors if
you are to use corresponding parts.

PyMVPA
------

The command line interface has been derived from the one of PyMVPA. The
configuration manager taken almost entirely from PyMVPA.

::

  Files: bin/testkraut, testkraut/cmdline/*, testkraut/config.py
  License: MIT
  Copyright: 2000-2012 PyMVPA developers

pyprov
------

Python implementation of the W3C's PROV-DM

::

  Author: Trung Dong Huynh <trungdong@donggiang.com>
  Files: testkraut/external/prov*.py
  License: MIT
  Copyright: 2012 University of Southampton

